:: Against-Wall-From-Behind-Dialogue [nobr]

<<if $sex.role == "Top">>
    <<= either(
        "You're standing behind _n.name as they brace themself against the $room.location."
    )>>
<<else>>
    <<= either(
        "You're braced against the $room.location with _n.name behind you."
        "_n.name leans you against the $room.location."
    )>>
<</if>>